### API 测试脚本
### 基础 URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. 测试用户相关 API

### 创建用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 获取所有用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 获取单个用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1

### 更新用户
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updateduser"
}

### 删除用户
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/1

### 2. 测试错误处理

### 获取不存在的用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/999

### 创建用户时缺少必填字段
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser"
}